<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM5.2">
<l>veḷḷai viḷicaṅ kiṭaṅkaiyiṟ koṇṭa vimala ṉeṉakkuruk kāṭṭāṉ</l>
<l>uḷḷam pukunteṉṉai naivittu nāḷu muyirpeytu kūttāṭṭuk kāṇuṅ</l>
<l>kaḷḷaviḻ ceṇpakap pūmalar kōtik kaḷitticai pāṭuṅ kuyilē</l>
<l>meḷḷa viruntu miḻaṟṟi miḻaṟṟāteṉ vēṅkaṭa vaṉvarak kūvāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The blemishless [Lord] who holds a white summoning conch in [His] left hand</l>
<l rend="indent">will not show Himself to me!</l>
<l>Entering [my] heart, causing distress to me [but] pouring life [into me],</l>
<l rend="indent">[He] would watch [my painful] dancing!</l>
<l>O koel that sings revelling [by] picking the blooming Champak flowers dripping</l>
<l rend="indent">with honey!</l>
<l>Staying [here] and speaking softing without prattling,</l>
<l rend="indent">cry so that my Lord of Veṅkaṭam comes!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
